  "texts": [
    "Prompts from 3 to 6 ask students to write an essay based on a text provided, and this type of essay is called response essay.",
    "The last two prompts, prompt 7 and 8, ask students to write an essay based on a situation which can be defined as a narrative essays.",
    "The ASAP dataset has three prompts with trait features, namely prompt 2, 7, and 8.",
    "In prompt 2, the rubric guidelines are categorized into Domain 1 (Writing Applications) and Domain 2 (Language Conventions).",
    "Domain 1 is described by ideas and contents, organization, style, and voice."
